01,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/cfad482837fe3a7a6313d18299c00d22?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fcfc6d008c1f5e03ed3b1173832299728.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"cfad482837fe3a7a6313d18299c00d22","url":"https://api.github.com/users/birdyisme","html_url":"https://github.com/birdyisme","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/birdyisme/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/birdyisme/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/birdyisme/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/birdyisme/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/birdyisme/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/birdyisme/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/birdyisme/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/birdyisme/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/birdyisme/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2012-12-01t13:01:44z","updated_at":"2012-12-01t13:01:44z","body":"hi , i have the same issue.\r\nto solve it i have made these change on apps/gallery/lib/managers.php \r\n\r\nrewrite function getthumbnailinfo :\r\n\r\n```\r\npublic function getthumbnailinfo($path) {\r\n\t\t$arr = databasemanager::getinstance()->getfiledata($path);\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\tif (!$arr) {\r\n\t\t\tif (file_exists ($path)) {\r\n\t\t\t\t$size = getimagesize($path);\r\n\t\t\t\t$arr = databasemanager::getinstance()->setfiledata($path, $size[0], self::thumbnail_height);\r\n\t\t\t} else {\r\n\t\t\t\t\\oc_log::write(self::tag, 'file '.$path.' don\\'t exists', \\oc_log::warn);\r\n\t\t\t\treturn false;\r\n\t\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t\t$ret = array('filepath' => $arr['path'],\r\n\t\t\t\t\t 'width' => $arr['width'],\r\n\t\t\t\t\t 'height' => $arr['height']);\r\n\t\treturn $ret;\r\n\t}\r\n```\r\n\r\ni don't know if this is the best method, but it work ;-)\r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/13334246","h